content:
The Actionable Relationship Center (ARC) lets you view customers' relationships in an easy-to-navigate graph. ARC helps understand relationships among people and businesses by presenting them in interactive components. Build graphs with standard and custom objects, then add the ARC Relationship Graph component to page layouts.

There are two versions of ARC available:

New ARC:
This version creates and views custom ARC relationship graphs and pre-configured templates.
Available components: 
ARC Details Panel
ARC Highlights Panel
ARC Relationship Graph
ARC Einstein Relationships Insights

Original ARC:
This version views pre-configured ARC relationship graphs.
Available components: 
ARC Financial Services Cloud

Set Up Actionable Relationship Center Permissions to start building relationship graphs. Create custom ARC Relationship Graphs with objects important to your users and add the ARC Relationship Graph component to record pages.

View Preconfigured ARC Relationship Graphs for Financial Services Cloud (Original ARC) by adding the ARC Financial Services Cloud component to record pages.
title: Actionable Relationship Center (ARC) Configuration Guide
